    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Gema Grahasarana Tbk operates as an interior contractor, and furniture manufacturer and distributor in Indonesia and internationally. The company operates through Interior, Furniture, Mechanical and Electrical; and Distribution and Trade segments. It offers interior fit-outs, furniture and panel manufacturing, mechanical and electrical installation, maintenance, and logistics services. The company offers customized wooden furniture, panels, office furniture, metal, and rattan; and home and office furnishing products. Further, it is involved in the trading of laminated material interior and furniture; house, and office furniture and equipment; and interior and furniture components, as well as setting up living, working, commercial, and hospitality spaces. The company was founded in 1984 and is headquartered in Tangerang, Indonesia. PT Gema Grahasarana Tbk is a subsidiary of PT Virucci Indogriya Sarana.",
